<h2>A Simple Weekly Meal Prep System</h2>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Day</th><th>Prep Task</th><th>Time</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Sunday</td><td>Cook grains, bake proteins, chop vegetables, prep breakfast jars</td><td>60–90 min</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Wednesday</td><td>Quick mid-week refresh: cook fresh protein, restock vegetables</td><td>20–30 min</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Daily</td><td>Assemble meals from prepped components (2–5 min)</td><td>2–5 min</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
